       <div id="content_Content_QuizListDiv"> 
        <div class="health_topic_content"> 
         <div class="pageTitle" id="top-of-page"> 
          <h1>Health Quizzes</h1> 
          <p>This page includes all of the healthfinder quizzes. Each quiz is full of resources and tips to help you make healthy changes today!</p> 
         </div> 
         <div class="shadow-wide"></div> 
         <div class="child_items"> 
          <div id="content_Content_QuizList_quiz_leftcol" class="quiz-leftcol"> 
           <div id="content_Content_QuizList_quizRepeater_quiz_0" class="box-left-healthtopic quizWrapper quiz-3"> 
            <div class="quiz-box clearfix"> 
             <h2 style="clear:left;">Everyday Healthy Living Quiz</h2> 
             <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">Theres a lot to know when it comes to everyday healthy living. Take this quiz to learn about important health topics and get tips to keep you on track  today and every day.</p> 
             <a class="button" href="/HealthTopics/Quiz/Question/everyday-healthy-living-quiz/">Start Quiz</a> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
           <div id="content_Content_QuizList_quizRepeater_quiz_1" class="box-left-healthtopic quizWrapper quiz-19"> 
            <div class="quiz-box clearfix"> 
             <h2 style="clear:left;">Stay Healthy As You Grow Older</h2> 
             <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">Theres a lot you can do to keep yourself healthy and feeling great in your 60s, 70s, and beyond. Take this quiz to get some tips on how to do it.</p> 
             <a class="button" href="/HealthTopics/Quiz/Question/everyday-healthy-living-older-adults/">Start Quiz</a> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
          <div id="content_Content_QuizList_quiz_rightcol" class="quiz-rightcol"> 
           <div id="content_Content_QuizList_quizGroupRepeater_quiz_group_0" class="box-right-healthtopic quizGroupWrapper quiz-group-1"> 
            <div class="quiz-box clearfix"> 
             <h2 style="clear:left;">Parenting Quizzes</h2> 
             <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">There's a lot to know about raising healthy kids! Take one of these quizzes to get helpful tips and resources about parenting.</p> 
             <div class="quiz_group_quizzes"> 
              <a class="button" href="/HealthTopics/Quiz/Question/parenting-quiz-first-year-of-life/">First Year of Life</a>
              <a class="button" href="/HealthTopics/Quiz/Question/parenting-quiz-ages-1-to-4/">Ages 1 to 4</a>
              <a class="button" href="/HealthTopics/Quiz/Question/parenting-quiz-ages-5-to-10/">Ages 5 to 10</a>
              <a class="button" href="/HealthTopics/Quiz/Question/parenting-quiz-ages-11-to-17/">Ages 11 to 17</a> 
             </div> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
          </div>
